For my darling
You’re my sun and my moon, you warm my soul and brighten my life just like you
keep mesmerizing me and making me fall in love with you more and more with every
second that passes by. Although I haven’t felt your touch and embrace yet, my body
feels the overwhelming need to melt into you, to just surrender for your love and die
in your arms. The love I hold for you carves a never ending hole in my chest that
makes me long for you and for your warmth, it makes me want to enjoy the simplest
little moments that life has to offer with you, and just take every breath I have left on
this earth next to you. The happiness you keep bringing into my life is immeasurable,
and no matter how hard I could ever try, I would never be able to give you a tiny bit of
it back. You have become more than just the reason I’m living, you’re my life, you are
everything I have known and will ever know, anything I will do in life will be for you,
because my entire existence means nothing without you. I love you with every bit of
me and my love for you will continue to grow forevermore.
